  //  * - Input1: Authorized contract's UTXO + tokenAmount1
  //  * 
  //  * @outputs
  //  * - Output0: Minting NFT back to the Registry contract + tokenAmount (tokenAmount0 + tokenAmount1)
  //  * - Output1: Authorized contract's UTXO back to the Registry contract
  //  * - Output2: Change BCH
  //  */
